<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I just ignore them. They give me tells..I never answer. They give me another tell..I dont answer. They get pissed at me and give me angry tells....I dont reply. I dont give them any indication that I even realize they have contacted me. I dont tell them no, I dont tell them they should go earn their stuff themselves, I dont tell them that begging is wrong, I dont answer them. I go on with my bussiness as if they werent even there. I dont tell them that there sob story sounds very..uhm ..er..sobby and that everyone has such stories and some of them might even be true. Mostly they dont bother me after the second tell that I ignore. I also have my inspection window thing reading as ....." What are you looking at? No I am not giving anything away! Especially to people who come running up inspecting me without asking!"</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
