<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Okay, to update I would like to tell you a story of what happened me today. I am sitting in QHills half way to BB trying to type out and /auction when a lvl 6 starts looking at my equipment. Which was fine. then I started seing a spame of "so and so is inspecting your equipment" pages and pages of it! So I left and went to BB. I sit down there to finish my auction and here he is again spamming me.  It was driving me crazy. Then you won't believe the first words out of his mouth were "do you have anything to give? I need your armor" OMG he spammed me, harrassed me and chased me to BB and then he begs from me? That is why I try to stay away from newbie areas.  I do remember however that some people are new to this game and don't know any better, so I simply told him "how would you like me to chase you around staring at your equipment over and over?" no response and he left. THANK GOODNESS! lol<hr>Dalass Daniels (Norrath Guardians of Honor)<br>
