And that s all! I dont think i am annoying by being like this and if anybody thinks that it can be annoying, please tell it to me.<br>
I think begging is a npart of Role Playing. But i can t stand beggars who harass the same character for hours. The character has worked to have his stuff and if he wants us to have an easier life, he will help us.<br>
I am only lvl 9 but i ALWAYS and i say ALWAYS help other troll, especially if they are SK like me, but it is because it is a very hard combo...<br>
